1
00:00:00,100 --> 00:00:01,680
It starts as an issue.

2
00:00:02,030 --> 00:00:05,120
Its own worktree. Its own real terminal.

3
00:00:05,470 --> 00:00:07,130
A dozen of these at once.

4
00:00:07,490 --> 00:00:11,780
It writes a plan — and stops. A second agent tries to refute it.

5
00:00:12,120 --> 00:00:13,250
Then it works.

6
00:00:13,600 --> 00:00:17,380
CI. Hygiene. Then a third agent reads the diff.

7
00:00:17,730 --> 00:00:19,560
Only what survives lands.

8
00:00:19,920 --> 00:00:22,710
And when it can't, it stops and tells you why.

9
00:00:23,510 --> 00:00:27,330
Shepherd runs many agents at once — and it is built to stop.
